Those pictures are screenshots of a game that is developed by @{"me" link "me" 0}
There is working engine but I didnt upload it because of lack of gfx.

This game @{U}should be@{UU}:

- Rogue-like, tured-based (or not, dunno yet) rpg

should have:

- tenths of spells, hundredths of monsters, caves, quests
- 640x256 or 640x480 gfx in 256 colours or more on gfx cards (if needed)
