- we'll see

Anyway this game will be close as its only possible to the paper-like rpg.
Im not sure it will be familiar to the any of the existing rpg system, or it
will be brand new rpg world. Dont know. It @{"depends on you" link "you" 0} too.

This idea should be developed ca. 10 years ago - i know that. But... i dont care.
If it will be no help from your side this game will not be finished at all.
(whow, what a relief...;)

Oh, yes.

This game as for now needs Amiga 040(030+fpu)+8mb free ram.
not much heh...

